    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Tiny Terraces” 是一个<strong>闲置农场游戏</strong>，你可以看到家伙做不同的任务在农场周围，因为你在游戏之外的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>种植作物：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种植庄稼，看着他们通过浇水、除草和收割来管理花园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136330/extras/14199aa96a49869a8bdbdc1a5f0e475d.poster.avif?t=1753981105\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136330/extras/14199aa96a49869a8bdbdc1a5f0e475d.webm?t=1753981105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136330/extras/14199aa96a49869a8bdbdc1a5f0e475d.mp4?t=1753981105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创造一些男人：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用特定的农作物和齿轮来制造更多的人来帮助管理农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136330/extras/9fdce604d82c571afbed791243a15685.poster.avif?t=1753981105\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136330/extras/9fdce604d82c571afbed791243a15685.webm?t=1753981105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136330/extras/9fdce604d82c571afbed791243a15685.mp4?t=1753981105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装饰：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用农作物生产的钱来购买装饰品来装饰你的农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136330/extras/aad36aa9ff5a141b284c888de65d70ee.avif?t=1753981105\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>请将我的游戏添加到您的愿望清单!</strong> :)</p>",
